and 'path_or_url2' are called 'path1' and 'path2' on this branch.
(diff_summarize_repos_repos): Huge semantic conflict here. The summarize
diff implementation in 1.7 does not use a separate set of diff callbacks.
So the code merged from trunk cannot even compile. Do not call the new code
that handles newly added/deleted diff targets in summarize mode for now.
This means that diff --summarize now fails for newly added or deleted
diff targets. This problem will be addressed in a separate commit.
